# Summary
Amplitude supports Single Sign-On (SSO) with SAML 2.0 providers including Auth0, G Suite, Azure AD, Okta, and OneLogin, allowing organizations to enforce SSO authentication, enable just-in-time provisioning for new users, and identify users via email addresses in SAML assertions.

# Keywords
- SAML 2.0 SSO providers
- Just-in-time provisioning
- Enterprise authentication
- SSO enforcement
- User identification via email
